  <brief_title>A Study of Pemetrexed Plus Carboplatin Combined With Radiation in Patients With Inoperable Locally Advanced Non-small Cell Lung Cancer (LA-NSCLC) (RT0801)</brief_title>
  <acronym>NSCLC</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase II Study of Pemetrexed Plus Carboplatin Combined With Radiation in Patients With Inoperable Locally Advanced Non-small Cell Lung Cancer</official_title>
